com.jlranta.pholiotracker.api

Interface StockApi

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlphaVantageApi, TestApi

    public interface StockApi
    StockApi is an interface that describes how the support for various stock APIs should be implemented. This makes it easier to add support for new APIs to the application.
    Author:
    Jarkko Lehtoranta
